column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq (up_ra, up_dec, #) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq (up_ra, up_dec, #) IS NOT # EXEC spExecuteSQL ' SELECT u.up_col0 as [col0], p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, dbo.fPhotoTypeN (p.type) as type, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, s.specObjID, s.z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.o
